{"tid":442457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李顯龍：準備好幾年內下台 未定接班人","createTime":"2017-10-20T15:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T17:26:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"854d4c03e88a788ebea09244ceeebaa96230b6d2","tid":442457,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171020/57355864\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171020%2F57355864&d=WlE0%2BH1Q2bB1Sc%2BZ6rwjmYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=502d6b91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20171020%2F57355864&h=48a1f433\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20171020/57355864</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171020/large/1508486509_9709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171020%2Flarge%2F1508486509_9709.jpg&h=fad4fd86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理李顯龍表示，他預計會在未來數年下台，目前未有接班人選，但會確保權力過渡暢順。<br />\n<br />\n李顯龍接受美國CNBC訪問，被問到是否已準備好在數年內下台，他回答：「是的，準備好了。」但繼任人方面，他坦承未有定案。「我相信這個人現時就在我們的內閣中，但到底這是誰，相信仍需要一段時間去判斷。」<br />\n<br />\n65歲的李顯龍是已故建國總理李光耀長子，2004年出任總理至今。他過往兩度治療癌症成功，但於去年一次演說中途突然不適，惹起外界對他健康以及繼任人選的揣測。<br />\n<br />\n美國CNBC/路透社"},{"pid":"9d5c3bb6f4f91282ded143d24bed97ecfb4573e1","tid":442457,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"李_ _"},{"pid":"b33b964be934d0df8fa81ba229e2cbf4e14a77db","tid":442457,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"世襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5a059e3aeeb30d7a0fa13e766fbad047a29c7","tid":442457,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-